data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, large study, 2 car garage home offers a spacious and inviting living space. The spacious kitchen has been updated with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Tile flooring throughout the home. Ceiling fans throughout home. The oversized primary suite has a large private bath with a separate shower and bath, double sinks and large walk-in closet. The upstairs game room will capture great memories for the family. Laundry room conveniently upstairs. Plenty backyard space with storage shed. NEWLY BUILT DECK, NEW FENCE, NEW A/C SYSTEM. Roof is 2 years old . Never flooded.   Come take a look today, this beautiful home won't last long!
